event CouldNotCloseTrade(address indexed trader, uint256 indexed pairIndex, uint256 index)

event OpenLimitUpdated(address indexed trader, uint256 indexed pairIndex, uint256 index, uint256 newPrice, uint256 newTp, uint256 newSl, uint256 maxSlippageP)
